abstract: >
  This repository provides a reproducible workflow for spatial transcriptomics analysis
  using SpotClean for spot decontamination and STdeconvolve for cell-type deconvolution.
  The workflow demonstrates spatial expression analysis on the Adult Mouse Brain FFPE
  dataset from 10x Genomics.

